parameter.description:
This variable determines how the red channel is generated based on the UV coordinates:
									 0 - Uses the X coordinate;
									 1 - Uses the Y coordinate;
									 2 - Uses the sum of X and Y coordinates.

This variable determines how the green channel is generated based on the UV coordinates:
									 0 - Uses the X coordinate;
									 1 - Uses the Y coordinate;
									 2 - Uses the sum of X and Y coordinates.

This variable determines how the blue channel is generated based on the UV coordinates:
									 0 - Uses the X coordinate;
									 1 - Uses the Y coordinate;
									 2 - Uses the sum of X and Y coordinates.
